<br>
7)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Rank structure does have power.  Disobedience to a guild officer in a reasonable situation can result in a broken paw council.  Officers and higher ranks are not allowed to order you to do unethical things, they are not allowed to give orders that are impossible or unethical (I.E Asking you to die so they can flee, asking you to camp items for them etc. . .).  It is the opinion of the guild that orders should not ever be necessary.  As the team we are if something needs to be done it should be done because you where asked and should never be asked unless it is the right thing.   If you feel an officer is abusing power report it immediately.  <br>
<br>
