<br>
9)&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp Officers have ten positions available.   These represent the ten original elders.  As positions are available new officers will be selected.  The guild master will nominate the members that they believe to be the best for the position.  Then the Officers will vote to the guild leader for each open position and the votes will be tallied.  Though the nominated members don’t need to be present the officers have to be present at the meeting to vote.   <br>
<br>
